pages.text: There are many biomes still unclaimed by Dragons, Dwarves, and Humans. These remaining biomes span from mild and meadowed to cool and forested. Here you will find many more Villagers and Illagers and a wide variety of creatures, but fewer remnants of the modern dominant races.
